7. What topics will you cover in your training, and why? (This should be the bulk of the deliverable.)

Training Topics
  - What is CyberSecurity
  - How is SilverCorp At-Risk?
  - Remote Working Risks
  - Methods of Attack
  - Phishing
  - Spoofing
  - Malware
  - Password Attacks
How to protect your device and SilverCorp
How to report a threat


8. After you’ve run your training, how will you measure its effectiveness? 

The success of the Security Training and Awareness Program will be measured by the following KPI’s: 

Personnel Reporting
  - Percentage of participants who have or haven’t completed training
  - Training hours per employee
  - Employee pass/fail rate on the Security Assessment
  - Course completion rates within different departments.
  - Employee Interviews/surveys for feedback and progress
  - Percentage of satisfied employees and the ease of accessibility of training materials, content relevance, and the overall appeal of the content.

System Reporting
  - Number of reported suspicious events
  - Lost/Stolen devices
  - Results of any phishing campaigns
  - Review employee survey feedback
*Resource: https://terranovasecurity.com/measure-success-security-awareness-program/

